      "text": "\n\n  ->Software vulnerabilities (CVEs)\n  ->Missing security patches\n  ->Insecure network configurations\n  ->Exposed ports\n  ->Vulnerable container images",
      "fontSize": 20.91428571428572,
      "fontFamily": 5,
